trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The properties of the GridViewDesigner class provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.ActionLists%2A> property returns a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> object, which typically contains an object that is derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> class for each level in the inheritance tree of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Egenskaper for klassen GridViewDesigner inneholder følgende funksjonalitet: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.ActionLists%2A>returnerer en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>objektet, som vanligvis inneholder et objekt som er avledet av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>klasse for hvert nivå i treet arving av designer.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.ActionLists%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property returns a collection of formatting schemes for display in the **Auto Format** dialog box.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>Egenskapen returnerer en samling av formatering skjemaene for visning i den **automatisk Format** dialogboksen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property returns a collection of template groups for the fields of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control and the top-level <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> templates.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>Egenskapen returnerer en samling av malen grupper for feltene for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll og det øverste nivået <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>maler.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property always returns `true`, indicating that the designer creates a temporary copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>Egenskapen returnerer alltid `true`, som angir at det opprettes en midlertidig kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The methods of the GridViewDesigner class provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.DataBind%2A> method binds the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control to a design-time data source.
trans-unit.target: Metoder for klassen GridViewDesigner inneholder følgende funksjonalitet: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.DataBind%2A>metoden binding den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen til en datakilde for utforming.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.DataBind%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method returns the markup that is used to render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> at design time.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>Metoden returnerer markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.Initialize%2A> method prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.Initialize%2A>Metoden Klargjør utformeren for å vise, redigere, og utformer tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.OnClick%2A> method is called when a region of the design-time view of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.OnClick%2A>Metoden kalles når et område for utforming visningen for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.OnClick%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.OnSchemaRefreshed%2A> method is called when the schema of the data source of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> changes.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.OnSchemaRefreshed%2A>-Metoden når skjemaet for datakilden for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>endringer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.OnSchemaRefreshed%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> method is used to remove or add properties or to shadow properties of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>Metoden brukes til å fjerne eller legge til egenskaper eller skyggen egenskapene til det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>

trans-unit.source: Design-time editable regions are not supported in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control, so the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.SetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> methods have no functionality.
trans-unit.target: Utformingen redigerbare områder støttes ikke i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll, så <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.SetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A>metoder har ingen funksjonalitet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.SetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll eller en kopi av kontrollen på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the designer action list collection for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir designer handlingen listesamling for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the collection of predefined formatting schemes to display in the **Auto Format** dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir samling av forhåndsdefinerte formatering skjemaene skal vises i den **automatisk Format** dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection> object is populated from an XML-encoded member of an internal class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>Objektet er fylt ut fra en XML-kodet medlem av en intern klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> that contains the predefined schemes for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> som inneholder de forhåndsdefinerte skjemaene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Binds the associated control to the design-time data source.
trans-unit.target: Tilknyttede kontrollen bindes til datakilden utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The DataBind method binds the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control to the design-time data source and assigns a unique value to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion.DesignerRegionAttributeName> field of each cell of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control's design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Databinde binding den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen utformingen datakilden og tilordne en unik verdi til den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion.DesignerRegionAttributeName>for hver celle i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollens utformingen gjengivelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion.DesignerRegionAttributeName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The `dataBoundControl` parameter is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control that is associated with this designer, or a copy of that control.
trans-unit.target: Den `dataBoundControl` parameteren er av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen som er tilknyttet utformeren eller en kopi av denne kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref> to bind to the design-time data source.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref> skal bindes til datakilden utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to render the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method does the following: 1.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetDesignTimeHtml gjør følgende: 1.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A> property of the control to `true`, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A> property is empty.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A>kontrollen til `true`, hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A>-egenskapen er tom.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A>

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.DataKeyNames%2A> property of the control to `null`, if the schema of the data source cannot be obtained.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.DataKeyNames%2A>kontrollen til `null`, hvis ikke kan hente skjemaet for datakilden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.DataKeyNames%2A>

trans-unit.source: Refreshes the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> object to force the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> method to be called.
trans-unit.target: Oppdaterer den <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>objekt for å fremtvinge det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>metoden kalles.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: Calls the base method to generate the markup.
trans-unit.target: Kaller base-metoden for å generere koden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the markup used to render the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref> at design time.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder markup brukes til å gjengi den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref> under utformingen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to render the associated control at design time and populates a collection of designer regions.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede kontrollen på utformingstidspunktet og fyller ut en samling av designer områder.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml> method to generate the markup for the design-time rendering of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall GetDesignTimeHtml den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml>metode for å generere markup utformingen gjengivelse av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.GridViewDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml>

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml also populates `regions` with a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion> object for each clickable or selectable region of the design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: GetDesignTimeHtml også fyller ut `regions` med en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion>objekt for hvert klikke eller valgbar område på utformingen gjengivelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>, the first cell in each row is selectable; all the cells in the rows are clickable.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>, den første cellen i hver rad velges; alle cellene i radene er klikke.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> to which definitions of the selectable and clickable regions in the design-time view of the control are added.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref> skal legges til som definisjoner av valgbar og klikke områder i visningen for utforming for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the markup used to render the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref> at design time.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder markup brukes til å gjengi den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref> under utformingen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Returns the content for an editable region of the design-time view of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer innholdet for en redigerbare området for utforming visningen for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This functionality is currently not available.
trans-unit.target: Denne funksjonaliteten er ikke tilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> for which to fetch content.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> å hente innhold.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Forbereder utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The designer host calls the Initialize method when it is ready to use the designer to render the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer verten kaller i initialiseringsmetoden når den er klar til å bruke designer til å gjengi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The Initialize and its base methods configure properties and set up events that are necessary for the operation of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Initialiseringen og tilhørende base metoder Konfigurer egenskaper og hendelser som er nødvendige for operasjonen av designer.

trans-unit.source: The `component` parameter is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control that is associated with this designer, or a copy of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Den `component` parameteren er av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen som er tilknyttet utformeren eller en kopi av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref>, which implements an <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref>, som implementerer en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Called when a region of the design-time view of the associated control is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når et område for utforming visningen for den tilknyttede kontrollen klikkes.

trans-unit.source: The OnClick method saves the selected region index and updates the markup that renders the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnClick lagrer valgt område indeksen og oppdateringer markup som gjengir den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs"></xref> that defines the clicked region of the control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs"> </xref> som definerer klikket område for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Called when the schema of the data source for the associated control changes.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når skjemaet for datakilden for den tilknyttede kontrollen endres.

trans-unit.source: Unless the designer is in template-editing mode or a field is being added or edited, the OnSchemaRefreshed method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InvokeTransactedChange%2A> method, which in turn calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> method to update the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control to reflect the data source change.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre designer er i modus for redigering av maler, eller et felt som legges til eller redigere metodekall OnSchemaRefreshed den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InvokeTransactedChange%2A>metoden som kaller den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>metode for å oppdatere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen for å gjenspeile endringen i datakilden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InvokeTransactedChange%2A>

trans-unit.source: Used by the designer to remove properties from or add additional properties to the display in the **Properties** grid or to shadow properties of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Brukes av designer Fjern egenskaper fra eller legge til flere egenskaper i visningen i den **Egenskaper** rutenett eller skyggen egenskapene for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Control designers use methods that are derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to shadow various control properties with corresponding design-time properties that the designer implements, and to add properties to or remove properties from the **Properties** grid.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen utviklere bruker metodene som er avledet fra den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden skyggelegge ulike egenskaper for kontroll med tilsvarende utformingen egenskaper som designer implementerer, og du kan legge til egenskaper til eller Fjern egenskaper fra den **Egenskaper** rutenett.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control, the PreFilterProperties method sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute> object of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A> property to `false` when the control is in template mode.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollerer PreFilterProperties metoden angir den <xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute>objekt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A>egenskapen `false` når kontrollen er i modus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: This is so a column that is in template mode cannot be deleted using the **Fields** dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Dette er så en kolonne som er i modus for ikke kan slettes med den **felt** dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: A collection implementing the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> of the added and shadowed properties.
trans-unit.target: En samling implementering av <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>av egenskapene tillagt og skyggelagt.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of sample rows for the associated control to display.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antall rader som utvalg for den tilknyttede kontrollen skal vises.

trans-unit.source: If the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control allows paging and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A> property is greater than 0, the SampleRowCount property returns the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A> plus 1 (but not greater than 100).
trans-unit.target: Hvis den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen kan bla og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A>egenskapen er større enn 0, returnerer egenskapen SampleRowCount den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A>plus 1 (men ikke større enn 100).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> does not allow paging or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A> is 0, SampleRowCount returns `5`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>tillater ikke bla eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A>er 0, returnerer SampleRowCount `5`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.PageSize%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The number of sample rows.
trans-unit.target: Antall rader i eksemplet.

trans-unit.source: Specifies content for an editable region of the design-time view for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Angir innholdet for en redigerbare området for utforming visningen for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The SetEditableDesignerRegionContent method has no functionality; there is no support for editable regions in the design-time view of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetEditableDesignerRegionContent har ingen funksjonalitet. Det er ikke støtte for redigerbare områder i utformingen visning av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> to update.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> å oppdatere.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> to write to `region`.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>ikke skrive til `region`.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a collection of template groups for the fields of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en samling av malen grupper for feltene for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property constructs a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> objects, one for each templated data field and one for each control template (pager and empty data) in the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups bygger en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>objekter, én for hvert organisasjonsapper datafelt og én for hver kontrollmal (personsøker og tom data) i den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>

trans-unit.source: The data field <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> elements have a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> object for each of the predefined row template types.
trans-unit.target: Data-feltet <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>elementer ha en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition>objekt for hver av de forhåndsdefinerte malen radtyper.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>

trans-unit.source: The control template <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> elements contain a single <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition>.
trans-unit.target: Den kontrollen malen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>elementer inneholde én <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> containing an element for each templated field in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> som inneholder et element for hvert organisasjonsapper felt i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer til å generere utformingen markup.

trans-unit.source: The UsePreviewControl property is always `true`, the designer uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that contains a copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen UsePreviewControl er alltid `true`, designer bruker en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>kontroll som inneholder en kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control does not affect any persistence for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>Kontrollen påvirker ikke noen utholdenhet for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: If the UsePreviewControl property has been overridden to return `false`, the designer will use the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> itself to generate the design-time markup, and design-time changes to the control will persist to the page markup source.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen UsePreviewControl er overstyrt for å returnere `false`, designer bruker den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>selve å generere utformingen markup, og endre utformingen kontrollen vil beholde siden markup kilde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer til å generere utformingen markup; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
